added.title: Mutiny for the Bounty
added.description: While Phil and Grandpa Max tune-up the Omni-Copter, a restless Ben takes the Rustbuggy off road, but when he is suddenly captured by Textrax and the hunter takes the bounty for himself, our hero must not only escape but avoid the wrath of the double-crossed Kraab and Sixsix!

added.title: The Chupaca-bro
added.description: Team Tennyson discovers that a small village's goats are being terrorized by the legendary Chupacabra, but when Ben realizes it's actually Dr. Animo, our hero must thwart the dastardly doctor before he uses the essence of the goats to power up into an unstoppable form!

added.title: Buggy Out
added.description: After winning a Sumo Slammers Champion belt, Ben returns to the Rustbucket to find his prize in the arms of Kevin, but when his rival hijacks the Rustbuggy instead, our hero must stop at nothing to get back what's rightfully his!

added.title: Introducing Kevin 11
added.description: At a local swap meet, Ben instead sets his sights on a Sumo Slammer collectible, but when Kevin takes it for himself, our hero must get it back by overcoming Kevin's secret weapon: an 11th alien!

added.title: Four by Four
added.description: During their visit to Twin City, Ben and Gwen sign up for some Laser Town awesomeness, but when Ben is teamed up with Kevin, the two must overcome their differences if they are to end up on top!

added.title: Tiger Fail
added.description: Gwen refuses to be pressured into choosing an ice cream flavor that she does not want.

added.title: A Ninjustice to Harold
added.description: Harold's world is turned upside down when Beth becomes the class ninja.

added.title: Having the Timeout of Our Lives
added.description: Owen forms a special bond with Duncan after having loads of fun with him during their timeouts.

added.title: Hic Hic Hooray
added.description: Bridgette gets the hiccups and becomes desperate to get rid of them.

added.title: Bananas & Cheese
added.description: Duncan is determined to stop the musical duo Bananas & Cheese from coming to the daycare.

added.title: Christmas Spirit
added.description: Apple & Onion have to become mall Santas to get the gifts they want for Christmas.

added.title: Wasted True Potential
added.description: In the wake of the previous season's victory, the ninja have gone soft and Master Wu must remind them of who they truly are.

added.title: Questing For Quests
added.description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

added.title: A Rocky Start
added.description: The ninja have found their quest! Now they just have to get there, which involves a road trip through the Desert of Doom, a region supposedly inhabited by a giant scarab beetle.

added.title: The Belly of the Beast
added.description: To repair the Land-Bounty, the ninja must retrieve a critical engine component that has been swallowed by a giant scarab beetle.

added.title: Booby-Traps, and How To Survive Them
added.description: The ninja team up with a reluctant Clutch Powers to enter a mysterious pyramid where they inadvertently unleash an ancient evil.

added.title: Oddities
added.description: When a mysterious carnival barker fuses V&V together, they must find a way to come unstuck.

added.title: I……am Vampier
added.description: When Vic enters the Monte Macabre film festival, he gets insecure about his artistic vision and decides to copy the work of others, but ultimately learns that staying true to yourself is what's most important.

added.title: Victor the Predictor
added.description: When Victor becomes convinced he has a special talent as a psychic, he decides to use his new mental abilities to counsel those around him - until one piece of advice goes too far.

added.title: Kindred Spirits
added.description: When Val becomes friends with the ghost of a silent film star, their friendship turns out to have dire consequences.

added.title: Decoding Valentino
added.description: When Val goes on an adventure with Isabella to decode an ancient language, he has to come to terms with the fact that Isabella is smarter in order to save himself.

added.title: Thunder Road
added.description: When a crate containing fifty Swords of Omen lands on Third Earth, the ThunderCats rush out in the ThunderTank to find them. Unfortunately The Mutants and Mumm-Ra want those swords too so it's going to be a race to get to them! A wacky race, you might say. We won't say that, but you might.

added.title: Sunken Treasure
added.description: A relaxing beach day becomes an underwater adventure when Unikitty and her friends find a message in a bottle.

added.title: Dawn of the Donut
added.description: Dr. Fox's plans to deliver donuts all over the Unikingdom are sidetracked by Unikitty's reluctance to follow instructions.

added.title: P.L.O.T. Device 2: Beyond the Bored Dome
added.description: Dr. Fox reprograms the P.L.O.T. Device to only generate boring events, but the gang can't help but add drama and excitement to every scenario.

added.title: Attack of Thermometron 9000
added.description: Axel must wrangle Galileo and Bobbie to shut down a rogue thermostat - improperly upgraded by Slobot - as it plunges the house into extreme hot and cold zones.

added.title: The Dynamo Dynamic
added.description: Axel finds himself at the center of a disagreement between Sarge and Masko over what's more important in battle - the weapon or the one who wields it - after Dynamo bonds the trio together!

added.title: The Best Friend/Thief and Brawler
added.description: The Best Friend: The top four brawlers in the Bakugan Battle League have been decided. For this round of the semi-finals it's a battle of best friends: Wynton vs. Dan. The winner of this battle between best buddies will move on to the championship round./Thief and Brawler: In the final battle of the Bakugan Battle league semi-finals it's Shun vs. Ajit. It's a grueling battle of focus, will, and strength, only a true brawler to emerge victorious.

added.title: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit/Secrets Exposed
added.description: Final Battle! Dan vs. Ajit: It's time for the event everyone in Los Volmos has been waiting for, The Bakugan Battle League finals! It's the Awesome Brawler's Dan Kouzo vs. the golden Bakugan brawler Ajit, these two face-off in a final brawl for it all./Secrets Exposed: The Bakugan Battle League has ended, and the winner has been determined, but the celebration is cut short when Phantom Thief Storm crashes the party by stealing everyone's Bakugan! It's up to Dan and Ajit to stop Storm and return all the stolen Bakugan.

added.title: Here Comes Haavik/The Fusion Bakugan Arrive
added.description: Here Comes Haavik: An evil shapeshifting alien has landed in Los Volmos! If that wasn't bad enough, he has a group of robot mechanoids on his trail trying to bring him justice. Meanwhile, Dan has accepted a battle challenge from a pair of brawlers, Chad and Trey./The Fusion Bakugan Arrive: Still humiliated by their defeat, Chad and Trey challenge Dan to rematch but this time they have a few tricks up their sleeve, and a little help on their side.

added.title: The Director/Queen Ebony
added.description: The Director: Everett Ray reaches out to Lia with an opportunity that seems too good to be true. Everett is now working in show business and proposes to make Lia's dream of becoming a film director come true. He's taken care of all the arrangements; all Lia has to do is provide the directorial vision./Queen Ebony: On his daily jaunt, Lightning learns of a street cat named Ebony, who's been treating dogs like servants, threatening them to do her bidding or face the wrath of her Bakugan! Lightning tries to reason with Ebony but when that doesn't work, it turns into a cat vs. dog Bakugan brawl!

added.title: Sophie, the Bakuganist/Midnight Train Battle!
added.description: Sophie, the Bakuganist: Magnus is on the trail of the illegal Baku-brawling devices and, is looking to cut off the supply at its source. When he witnesses an illegal deal going down, he knows it's up to him to go after the shipment to keep the illegal devices off the street./Midnight Train Battle!: Sophie Judson Warfield, a wealthy activist with the Citizens to Save Bakugan Society, is working to put an end to all Bakugan brawling. Her latest target is the Awesome Brawlers themselves. When Wynton doesn't take Sophie seriously, the encounter quickly turns into an all-out Bakugan brawl.

added.title: Enter the Wood Man
added.description: Mega Man accidentally awakens Wood Man, who thinks it's still the Hard Age, sets off on a path of destruction toward Silicon City.

added.title: Lightfall Part 1
added.description: The mysterious Lord Obsidian calls Mega Man a traitor to robots and challenges him to a duel. An overconfident Mega Man is humbled by this mysterious new villain.

added.title: Lightfall Part 2
added.description: Lord Obsidian attacks the Lighthouse, but Mega Man overcomes his insecurity and works with his family to repel the big bad, who's rescued at the last second by a mysterious lieutenant, Namagem.

added.title: Rush to Greatness
added.description: Rush puts his new battle upgrades to the test in a battle with Wave Man.

added.title: Swish
added.description: Namagem attacks Mega Man using a variety of powers, revealing that they both can replicate schematics. However, Namagem can carry more than three at a time! The true beginning of the mysterious villain's arc begins here.

added.title: Alien Hunt! With Meteorfire and Cosmos Part 1
added.description: Bumblebee enlists washed-up TV show host Meteorfire to help him find another of Windblade's psychic shards on Luna-3.

added.title: Alien Hunt! With Meteorfire and Cosmos Part 2
added.description: Bumblebee runs the gauntlet of creepily haunted Luna-3, while Meteorfire records everything on camera for his show.

added.title: Huelga por el Botin
added.description: Mientras Phil y el abuelo Max afinan el Omni-Copter, Ben, inquieto, saca el Rustbuggy de la carretera. Pero cuando de repente es capturado por Tetrax, nuestro héroe no solo debe escapar, sino también evitar la ira de los traicioneros Kraab y SeiSeis.

added.title: Presentando a Kevin 11
added.description: En un encuentro de intercambio local, Ben se interesa en un coleccionable de Luchadores de Sumo. Pero cuando Kevin se apodera del objeto, nuestro héroe debe superar el arma secreta de Kevin para recuperarlo: iun 11º extraterrestre!

added.title: Paseo en Buggy
added.description: Después de ganar un cinturón como campeón de Luchadores de Sumo, Ben regresa al Rustbucket y encuentra su premio en los brazos de Kevin. Pero cuando su rival secuestra el Rustbuggy, inuestro héroe no debe detenerse ante nada para recuperar lo que le pertenece legítimamente!

added.title: El Chupacabro
added.description: El equipo Tennyson descubre que las cabras de una pequeña aldea están siendo aterrorizadas por el legendario Chupacabra. Pero cuando Ben se da cuenta de que en realidad se trata del Dr. Ánimo, nuestro héroe debe frustrar al malvado médico.

added.title: Cuatro por Cuatro
added.description: Durante su visita a Ciudad Gemelos, Ben y Gwen se inscriben en una competencia de laser-tag. Pero cuando Ben se une a Kevin, los dos deben superar sus diferencias si quieren terminar en la cima.

added.title: Potencial Desperdiciado
added.description: A raíz de la victoria de la temporada anterior, los ninjas se han ablandado y el Maestro Wu debe recordarles quiénes son realmente.

added.title: Buscando Misiones
added.description: Al darse cuenta de que se han ablandado, el ninja busca una misión para reactivar su entrenamiento de Spinjitzu. Desafortunadamente, la ciudad de NINJAGO está disfrutando de un período de rara tranquilidad.

added.title: Un Comienzo Dificil
added.description: iLos ninja han encontrado su búsqueda! Ahora solo tienen que llegar allí, lo que implica un viaje por carretera a través del desierto de Doom, una región supuestamente habitada por un escarabajo gigante.

added.title: El Vientre del Monstruo
added.description: Para reparar el Land-Bounty, el ninja debe recuperar un componente crítico del motor que ha sido tragado por un escarabajo gigante.

added.title: #LosConejosMágicos
added.description: Cuando Zee le pide a Kara que cuide a sus dos conejitos mágicos, pronto comienzan a multiplicarse y a desatar el caos por toda Metrópolis.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Trampas y Como Sobrevivir a Ellas
added.description: El ninja se une a un clutch Powers renuente para entrar en una misteriosa pirámide donde desatan sin darse cuenta un antiguo mal.

added.title: #TrianguloDeOdio
added.description: Cuando la exnovia de Hal aparece en el partido de bienvenida de la preparatoria Metrópolis y se enfurece por amor, convertida en la villana Star Sapphire, Jessica comienza a cuestionar sus propias tácticas no violentas.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Fallo de tigre
added.description: Gwen se niega a que la presionen para elegir un sabor de helado que no quiere.

added.title: Una ninja justicia para Harold
added.description: El mundo de Harold queda de cabeza cuando sus compañeros declaran que Beth es la verdadera ninja de la clase.

added.title: El castigo de mi vida
added.description: Owen forma un nexo especial con Duncan después de que ambos se divirtieran mucho durante sus castigos.

added.title: Hip hip Hurra
added.description: Bridgette tiene hipo y está desesperada por librarse de ellos.

added.title: Bananas y Queso
added.description: Duncan está decidido a evitar que el dúo Banana y Queso se presente en la guardería.

added.title: La Dinamica del Dinamo
added.description: iAxel se encuentra en el centro de un desacuerdo entre Sarge y Masko sobre lo que es más importante en la batalla, el arma o el que lo maneja, después de que Dynamo une al trío!

added.title: Ataque de Thermometron 9000
added.description: Axel debe lidiar con Galileo y Bobbie para apagar un termostato deshonesto, que Slobot actualizó incorrectamente, ya que sumerge la casa en zonas extremadamente frías y calientes.
